name: E-Transfair
overview:
E-TransFair GmbH builds, supports, and runs some of the most powerful and engaging content, networking, and e-commerce destinations on the Internet.

We are an IT company based in Leonberg, Germany. Over the past years, we developed more than 50 websites and applications for customers from seven countries, in five different languages. We have experience in web development of corporate websites, web 2.0, social networking, and e-commerce.

E-Transfair is involved in none profit and for profit business: Our current focus is on creating user friendly price comparison and visual comparison of niche products (f.i. perfume, watches). We work with affiliate platforms such as Commission Junction, Link Share, Google Affiliates. E-TransFair is strongly involved in none profit projects in order to raise money for people in need and to connect people around the world. We believe that it is our corporate responsibility to use our expertise to help others and we therefore donate all income from these projects and cover the running cost of the platforms.
